Hello Guys,

I made a new Map called bhop_simplewhite.
Like it says in the name i tried to keep it as simple as possible.
If you find some bugs you can always report the bug in the comment section.

      About the map:

  • This map has 6 stages.
  • This map is a Tier 2
  • You could run this map in under 40 seconds.
  • I made this map in 4 days.
  • This map contains a bonus
If you want you can send me your runs of this map and i'll put it in the desc.

Have fun playing it!

PS. If you want the Textures for your Server then this is what you need:
https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1891025237
